data.description: Situated on a private, level lot on the Mon-Yough Trail, this 2 bed 1 bath home is great adventure for all hikers, bikers, and even boaters! The home is just along the Yough River and features an updated kitchen, new windows, new washer, dryer, hardwood floors, 10x16 deck, gazebo, and shed. It contains a one car garage with a large storage area for canoes, kayaks, or bikes! It also has 4 off-street parking spaces. The house included a gas furnace and central air. Located in Elizabeth Forward School District.
